After living for several months with a parasite that fed off me, I was finally able to undergo a painful procedure for removing it.



Then they forced the screaming, squealing parasite into my hands expecting me to care for it.

“It's a boy,” they said excitedly.
c:
The intoxicated alien comes everyday and tries to inject more parasites in me.
